elvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\" mpa-font-style=\"mgpd54c3gys\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"letter-spacing: 1px;font-weight: bold;\">知识共享协议（MEK）：</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"letter-spacing: 1px;\">标准化跨Agent的知识、经验、工具的共享和复用机制。</span></span></p>\n   </li>\n  </ul>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 24px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:15px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\" mpa-font-style=\"mgpd54c3irb\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"letter-spacing: 1px;\">这三大标准为构建一个开放、可互操作的智能体生态系统奠定了坚实的技术基石。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\" nodeleaf=\"\" data-mpa-action-id=\"mgqn63k23n9\" data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\"><img data-imgfileid=\"505150496\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img js_insertlocalimg\" data-ratio=\"0.70625\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1280\" height=\"575\" style=\"width: 100%;background-color: transparent;\" type=\"block\" width=\"1080\" data-backw=\"578\" data-backh=\"408\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=31c370c0&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FUicQ7HgWiaUb0Hte1ibgObCpQM5nT6IMia2la92rPCLkDPI59GmBxZXOdEHoUAvcD5j17m4MUxrq9pPAvn0wU8hYeg%2F640%3Ffrom%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 24px;line-height: 1.75em;text-align: left;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:15px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;M